                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-806033960" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="806033960">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/junwk/">JUNWK1334</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2014-05-12</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">写得挺浅的，普通的科普读物，没有什么特别的见解和资料，大概因为这本书是面向西方读者的缘故……</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="827348569">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-827348569" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-827348569" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="827348569">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/RAKA/">野次馬</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2014-07-19</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">有趣的點：陰翳禮讚，水晶宮中初次展出的抽水馬桶，書院風格的普及與展開，資源有效型文化。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="412913667">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-412913667" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-412913667" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="412913667">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1524701/">拈花微笑</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2011-07-11</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">阅知日本系列之一。角度很有意思啊，不是讲明治，而是走德川。人口构成、饮食结构、穿着理念、对待排泄、居所的理解。有些东西似乎还需要更多了解，才能更清楚一下。但基本观点是，德川不现代，但人民未必不幸福。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

        

